contentTypes.name: Image
contentTypes.description: A pod for an image asset.

validations.message: Marks are not allowed
Only link to Url nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Callout
contentTypes.description: Pull quotes, "look at me" text. Not intended to be used as a banner or other "feature" content type.

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Only heading 2 and heading 3 nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Quote
contentTypes.description: Fields for content and attribution, so you can drop a pithy quote and tell people where it came from.

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Nodes are not allowed

contentTypes.name: Image Gallery
contentTypes.description: Collection of images to be displayed as a group

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Nodes are not allowed

contentTypes.name: Vine
contentTypes.description: A bundle of pods, grouped together into a larger story.

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Only heading 2, heading 3, heading 4, heading 5, heading 6, ordered list, unordered list, link to Url, quote, link to entry, block entry, and asset nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Page
contentTypes.description: Plain template with rich text content field for general website pages (rather than vine bundles)

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Only heading 2, heading 3, heading 4, heading 5, heading 6, ordered list, unordered list, quote, block entry, link to entry, inline entry, horizontal rule, and link to Url nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Link List
contentTypes.description: A collection of Link's, grouped together as a list.

contentTypes.name: Video
contentTypes.description: A pod for a video asset.

validations.message: Marks are not allowed
Only link to Url nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Audio
contentTypes.description: A pod for an audio asset.

validations.message: Marks are not allowed
Only link to Url nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Royal
contentTypes.description: A member of our very own Royals family.

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Only unordered list and ordered list nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Group
contentTypes.description: A collection of related Person entries. Examples include organisational teams (Royals Gangs/Partners, special project teams (Green Team) etc.

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Only unordered list and ordered list nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Gangs
contentTypes.description: Royals Gangs. A collection of each Group that represents one of the Gangs. You shouldn't need to edit this often, if at all. You more likely want to edit the members of a gang's Group, or the individual Royal entries.

contentTypes.name: Article
contentTypes.description: A blog post, opinion piece or other medium-to-long form article.

validations.message: Only bold and italic marks are allowed
Only heading 2, heading 3, heading 4, heading 5, heading 6, ordered list, unordered list, link to Url, quote, link to entry, block entry, and asset nodes are allowed

contentTypes.name: Office
contentTypes.description: Location and contact information for a Royals office.

validations.message: Only numbers, capital letters and dashes "-" are allowed.
Must be a valid phone number format starting with either a digit or "+" if you want to include international code. Capital letters are allowed if you want something like 1800-PIZZA-TIME
